{"text_id":48419,"tokens":["As","ymmetric"," super","conductivity"," emerges"," in"," metallic"," systems"," when"," their"," electronic"," properties"," exhibit"," spatial"," variations","."," This"," phenomenon"," defies"," the"," conventional"," wisdom"," of"," homogeneous"," super","conductivity",","," where"," electrons"," pair"," up"," symmetric","ally","."," Our"," work"," investigates"," the"," mechanisms"," leading"," to"," this"," asymmetric"," behavior"," in"," various"," metallic"," systems","."," We"," employed"," diverse"," theoretical"," methods"," to"," unveil"," the"," microscopic"," origin"," of"," this"," effect","."," Our"," results"," demonstrate"," that"," the"," presence"," of"," strong"," local"," variations"," in"," the"," electronic"," density"," of"," states",","," such"," as"," those"," stemming"," from"," crystal"," imperfections"," or"," interfaces",","," induces"," spatial"," asymmetry"," in"," the"," superconducting"," pairing","."," We"," propose"," that"," the"," observed"," asymmetry"," arises"," from"," the"," interplay"," between"," local"," electronic"," correlations"," and"," the"," macroscopic"," magnetic"," field"," generated"," by"," the"," superconducting"," condensate","."," Our"," findings"," deepen"," our"," understanding"," of"," unconventional"," super","conductivity"," and"," its"," potential"," applications"," in"," various"," technological"," applications","."],"sub_source":"arxiv","model":"gemma-7b-it","label":1}